CatDescriptText: The headlines on the copies of The Pittsburgh Courier being held by men in image read, "Poll of Negro Delegates for Kennedy, Adlai", "Fourth in Series Governor Nelson Rockefeller" and "Big Auto ...[?] Shameful Atlantic".
TitMainTitle: Two seated men stuffing envelopes, another two men holding Far West Edition of The Pittsburgh Courier newspaper with Nelson Rockefeller on cover, and posters hanging on wall that read, "Meet a Winner Draft Rockefeller"
